function onload()
    setupObjects = {
        diceBag = "diceBag",
        favorBag = "favorBag",
        publicObjectives = "publicObjectives",
        privateObjectives = "privateObjectives",
        toolCards = "toolCards",
        setupButtons = "setupButtons",
        diceButtons = "diceButtons",
        windowGreen = "windowGreen",
        windowBlue = "windowBlue",
        windowRed = "windowRed",
        windowPurple = "windowPurple",
        sDice = "sDice",
        startingPlayerToken = "startingPlayerToken",
        currentPlayerToken = "currentPlayerToken"
    }
    prefix = "[bffbf2][SAGRADA][-]"
    gameObjects = {}
    allObjects = getAllObjects()
    for o, object in ipairs(allObjects) do
        if #object.getTags() >= 1 then
            for t, tag in ipairs(object.getTags()) do
                if setupObjects[tag] ~= nil then
                    setupObjects[tag] = object
                end
            end
        end
        if object.hasTag("diagonalScore") then
            object.destruct()
        end
    end
    setupCardsIndex = 1
    cardSetupParameters = {
        {deck=setupObjects.publicObjectives, type="shuffle", position=0,             flip=true},
        {deck=setupObjects.publicObjectives, type="take",    position={-10,2.2,-1.5},flip=true},
        {deck=setupObjects.publicObjectives, type="take",    position={-6, 2.2,-1.5},flip=true},
        {deck=setupObjects.publicObjectives, type="take",    position={-2, 2.2,-1.5},flip=true},
        {deck=setupObjects.toolCards,        type="shuffle", position=0,             flip=true},
        {deck=setupObjects.toolCards,        type="take",    position={10, 2.2,-1.5},flip=true},
        {deck=setupObjects.toolCards,        type="take",    position={6,  2.2,-1.5},flip=true},
        {deck=setupObjects.toolCards,        type="take",    position={2,  2.2,-1.5},flip=true},
        {deck=setupObjects.privateObjectives,type="shuffle", position=0,             flip=true},
        {deck=setupObjects.privateObjectives,type="deal",    position="Green",       flip=true},
        {deck=setupObjects.privateObjectives,type="deal",    position="Blue",        flip=true},
        {deck=setupObjects.privateObjectives,type="deal",    position="Red",         flip=true},
        {deck=setupObjects.privateObjectives,type="deal",    position="Purple",      flip=true},
    }
    createButtons()
    setupObjects.diceBag.addContextMenuItem("Dice for 2 [5 Dice]",  dice2)
    setupObjects.diceBag.addContextMenuItem("Dice for 3 [7 Dice]",  dice3)
    setupObjects.diceBag.addContextMenuItem("Dice for 4 [9 Dice]",  dice4)
    diceAmount = 5
    diceIndex = 1
    Wait.time(function() fillDice() end, 0.5, 1)
    Wait.time(function() shuffleWindowPatterns() end, 1, 1)

    startingTurn = 1
    currentTurn = 1
    turnOrder = {
        {colour = "Green", object = nil},
        {colour = "Blue", object = nil},
        {colour = "Red", object = nil},
        {colour = "Purple", object = nil},
    }
    setupObjects.startingPlayerToken.setLock(true)
    placeStartingPlayerToken()
    setupObjects.currentPlayerToken.setLock(true)
    placeCurrentPlayerToken()
    playerPrivateObjectives = {}
    playerPublicObjectives = {}
    gameStarted = false
end

function fillDice()
    setupObjects.sDice.setLock(false)
    setupObjects.sDice.setScale({0.5,0.5,0.5})
    local diceColours = {
        {255,228,74},--yellow
        {255,67,103},--red
        {130,255,66},--green
        {135,66,255},--purple
        {66,201,255},--blue
    }
    local diceColourStrings = {
        "yellow",
        "red",
        "green",
        "purple",
        "blue"
    }
    local colourIndex = 1
    setupObjects.diceBag.reset()
    setupObjects.sDice.setScale({0.5,0.5,0.5})
    for c, colours in ipairs(diceColours) do
        for d=1, 18, 1 do
            local newDice = setupObjects.sDice.clone()
            newDice.setColorTint({colours[1]/255,colours[2]/255,colours[3]/255,1})
            newDice.setGMNotes(diceColourStrings[c])
            setupObjects.diceBag.putObject(newDice)
        end
    end
    setupObjects.sDice.setLock(true)
    setupObjects.sDice.setScale({0,0,0})
end

function shuffleWindowPatterns()
    local windowPatterns = {setupObjects.windowGreen,setupObjects.windowBlue,setupObjects.windowRed,setupObjects.windowPurple}
    for w, window in ipairs(windowPatterns) do
        window.call("randomize")
        drawFavorTokens(window,tonumber(window.getGMNotes()))
    end
end

function onObjectLeaveContainer(container, object)
    if object.type == "Generic" then
        Wait.time(function() object.use_snap_points = true end, 0.5, 1)
    end
end

function enableSnap(object)
    object.use_snap_points = true
    --log(object.use_snap_points)
end

function setupCards()
    gameStarted = true
    Wait.time(function() setupCardsHandler() end, 0.15, #cardSetupParameters)
    setupObjects.setupButtons.destruct()
    local windowPatterns = {setupObjects.windowGreen,setupObjects.windowBlue,setupObjects.windowRed,setupObjects.windowPurple}
    for w, window in ipairs(windowPatterns) do
        --window.removeButton(0)
        window.editButton({index=0, width=0, label=""})
    end
end

function setupCardsHandler()
    if cardSetupParameters[setupCardsIndex].type == "shuffle" then
        cardSetupParameters[setupCardsIndex].deck.randomize()
    end
    if cardSetupParameters[setupCardsIndex].type == "take" then
        local p = Vector(cardSetupParameters[setupCardsIndex].position)
        local f = cardSetupParameters[setupCardsIndex].flip
        local takenCard = cardSetupParameters[setupCardsIndex].deck.takeObject({position=p,flip=f})
        if takenCard.getGMNotes() ~= "" or nil then
            table.insert(playerPublicObjectives, takenCard.getGMNotes())
        end
    end
    if cardSetupParameters[setupCardsIndex].type == "deal" then
        local c = cardSetupParameters[setupCardsIndex].position
        local takenCard = cardSetupParameters[setupCardsIndex].deck.takeObject({position={0,0,0}})
        table.insert(playerPrivateObjectives, takenCard.getGMNotes())
        takenCard.deal(1,c,1)
    end
    setupCardsIndex = setupCardsIndex + 1
end

function dice2() diceAmount = 5  editDiceButtonLabel() printToAll(prefix .. " Dice Amount set to 2 Players [5 Dice]") end
function dice3() diceAmount = 7  editDiceButtonLabel() printToAll(prefix .. " Dice Amount set to 3 Players [7 Dice]") end

function editDiceButtonLabel()
    setupObjects.diceButtons.editButton({index=0, label="ROLL " .. tostring(diceAmount) .. " DICE"})
end

function drawDice()
    diceIndex = 1
    Wait.time(function() drawDiceHandler() end, 0.1, diceAmount)
end

function drawDiceHandler()
    setupObjects.diceBag.randomize()
    local diceParameters = {position=Vector(0,2.5,11), rotation={0,0,0}}
    local diceOffsets = {{4,2,0,-2,-4},{6,4,2,0,-2,-4,-6},{8,6,4,2,0,-2,-4,-6,-8},}
    if diceAmount == 5 then diceParameters.position.x = diceOffsets[1][diceIndex] end
    if diceAmount == 7 then diceParameters.position.x = diceOffsets[2][diceIndex] end
    if diceAmount == 9 then diceParameters.position.x = diceOffsets[3][diceIndex] end
    local takenDice = setupObjects.diceBag.takeObject()
    takenDice.setPosition(diceParameters.position)
    Wait.time(function() takenDice.randomize() end, 1, 1)
    diceIndex = diceIndex + 1
end

function randomizeWindowPattern(object,player,alt_click)
    local difficulty = object.call("randomize")
    drawFavorTokens(object,difficulty)
end

function drawFavorTokens(object,amount)
    local previousTokens = findCast(Vector(object.getPosition()):add(Vector(0,0,5)),Vector(6,5,10),3)
    for f, favorToken in ipairs(previousTokens) do
        if favorToken.hit_object.hasTag("favortoken") then
            favorToken.hit_object.destruct()
        end
    end
    local o3 = {Vector(1.727,0.8,-4.08),Vector(0,0.8,-4.08),Vector(-1.727,0.8,-4.08)}
    local o4 = {Vector(2.47,0.8,-2.9),Vector(0.82,0.8,-2.9),Vector(-0.82,0.8,-2.9),Vector(-2.47,0.8,-2.9)}
    local o5 = {Vector(2.47,0.8,-2.9),Vector(0.82,0.8,-2.9),Vector(0,0.8,-4.1),Vector(-0.82,0.8,-2.9),Vector(-2.47,0.8,-2.9)}
    local o6 = {Vector(2.47,0.8,-2.9),Vector(0.82,0.8,-2.9),Vector(1.727,0.8,-4.08),Vector(-1.727,0.8,-4.08),Vector(-0.82,0.8,-2.9),Vector(-2.47,0.8,-2.9)}
    local targetOffsets = o3
    if amount == 3 then targetOffsets = o3 end
    if amount == 4 then targetOffsets = o4 end
    if amount == 5 then targetOffsets = o5 end
    if amount == 6 then targetOffsets = o6 end
    for o, offset in ipairs(targetOffsets) do
        local tokenPosition = object.positionToWorld(offset)
        setupObjects.favorBag.takeObject({position=tokenPosition})
    end
end

function findCast(pos,size,type)
    local hitList = Physics.cast({
        origin       = pos,
        direction    = {0,-0.01,0},
        type         = type,
        size         = size,
        max_distance = 100,
        debug        = false,
    })
    return hitList
end

function countScoreWrapper(object, player, alt)
    if gameStarted == false then
        printToAll(prefix .. " Game has not started.")
        return
    end
    local playerIndex = 1
    local windows = {
        setupObjects.windowGreen,
        setupObjects.windowBlue,
        setupObjects.windowRed,
        setupObjects.windowPurple,
    }
    for w, window in ipairs(windows) do
        if object == window then
            playerIndex = w
        end
    end
    local playerScores = countScore(playerPublicObjectives, playerPrivateObjectives[playerIndex], object)
    local playerScore = 0
    for s, score in ipairs(playerScores) do
        if score[2] == "Open Window Spaces" then
            playerScore = playerScore - score[1]
        else
            playerScore = playerScore + score[1]
        end
    end
    local playerPrefixStrings = {
        " [32FF6C]Player Green[-] has a total score of ",
        " [34B9FF]Player Blue[-] has a total score of ",
        " [FF3548]Player Red[-] has a total score of ",
        " [8831FF]Player Purple[-] has a total score of ",
    }
    local outputStrings = {prefix .. playerPrefixStrings[playerIndex] .. playerScore}
    for o, objective in ipairs(playerScores) do
        table.insert(outputStrings, "[bbbbbb]" .. objective[2] .. ": " .. objective[1] .. "[-]")
    end
    local totalString = ""
    for s, outputString in ipairs(outputStrings) do
        totalString = totalString .. outputString .. "\n"
    end
    printToAll(totalString)
end

function countScore(scoreTypes, shadeType, window)
    local shade = shadeType
    local scoreFlags = {
        lightShades =        false,
        mediumShades =       false,
        deepShades =         false,
        shadeVariety =       false,
        rowShadeVariety =    false,
        columnShadeVariety = false,
        colorVariety =       false,
        rowColorVariety =    false,
        columnColorVariety = false,
        colorDiagonals =     false,
    }
    for s, scoreType in ipairs(scoreTypes) do
        if scoreType == "Light Shades" then scoreFlags["lightShades"] = true end
        if scoreType == "Medium Shades" then scoreFlags["mediumShades"] = true end
        if scoreType == "Deep Shades" then scoreFlags["deepShades"] = true end
        if scoreType == "Shade Variety" then scoreFlags["shadeVariety"] = true end
        if scoreType == "Row Shade Variety" then scoreFlags["rowShadeVariety"] = true end
        if scoreType == "Column Shade Variety" then scoreFlags["columnShadeVariety"] = true end
        if scoreType == "Color Variety" then scoreFlags["colorVariety"] = true end
        if scoreType == "Row Color Variety" then scoreFlags["rowColorVariety"] = true end
        if scoreType == "Column Color Variety" then scoreFlags["columnColorVariety"] = true end
        if scoreType == "Color Diagonals" then scoreFlags["colorDiagonals"] = true end
    end
    local scoreOutput = {}
    local totalScore = 0
    local snapPosition = Vector(2.19,0.2,1.65)
    local snapOffsets = Vector(1.1,0,1.1)
    local snapPositions = {}
    for z = 0, 3, 1 do
        local snapRow = {}
        for x = 0, 4, 1 do
            local newSnap = Vector(snapPosition.x - (snapOffsets.x * x), snapPosition.y + snapOffsets.y, snapPosition.z - (snapOffsets.z * z))
            table.insert(snapRow, newSnap)
        end
        table.insert(snapPositions, snapRow)
    end
    local diceTable = {}
    for z = 1, 4, 1 do
        local diceRow = {}
        for x = 1, 5, 1 do
            local castPosition = window.positionToWorld(Vector(snapPositions[z][x]))
            local objectsAtPosition = findCast(castPosition:add(Vector(0,1,0)),Vector(1,1,1),1)
            for o, object in ipairs(objectsAtPosition) do
                if object.hit_object.hasTag("sDice") then
                    local diceParameters = {object.hit_object.getValue(), object.hit_object.getGMNotes()}
                    table.insert(diceRow, diceParameters)
                end
            end
        end
        table.insert(diceTable, diceRow)
    end
    if scoreFlags.colorDiagonals then
        local categoryScore = colorDiagonals(diceTable, snapPositions)
        local scoreTable = {tonumber(categoryScore),"Color Diagonals"}
        table.insert(scoreOutput, scoreTable)
    end
    if scoreFlags.columnColorVariety then
        local categoryScore = columnVariety(diceTable, snapPositions, "Color")
        local scoreTable = {tonumber(categoryScore),"Column Color Variety"}
        table.insert(scoreOutput, scoreTable)
    end
    if scoreFlags.columnShadeVariety then
        local categoryScore = columnVariety(diceTable, snapPositions, "Shade")
        local scoreTable = {tonumber(categoryScore),"Column Shade Variety"}
        table.insert(scoreOutput, scoreTable)
    end
    if scoreFlags.rowColorVariety then
        local categoryScore = rowVariety(diceTable, snapPositions, "Color")
        local scoreTable = {tonumber(categoryScore),"Row Color Variety"}
        table.insert(scoreOutput, scoreTable)
    end
    if scoreFlags.rowShadeVariety then
        local categoryScore = rowVariety(diceTable, snapPositions, "Shade")
        local scoreTable = {tonumber(categoryScore),"Row Shade Variety"}
        table.insert(scoreOutput, scoreTable)
    end
    if scoreFlags.lightShades then
        local categoryScore = shades(diceTable, snapPositions, "Light")
        local scoreTable = {tonumber(categoryScore),"Light Shades"}
        table.insert(scoreOutput, scoreTable)
    end
    if scoreFlags.mediumShades then
        local categoryScore = shades(diceTable, snapPositions, "Medium")
        local scoreTable = {tonumber(categoryScore),"Medium Shades"}
        table.insert(scoreOutput, scoreTable)
    end
    if scoreFlags.deepShades then
        local categoryScore = shades(diceTable, snapPositions, "Deep")
        local scoreTable = {tonumber(categoryScore),"Deep Shades"}
        table.insert(scoreOutput, scoreTable)
    end
    if scoreFlags.colorVariety then
        local categoryScore = variety(diceTable, snapPositions, "Color")
        local scoreTable = {tonumber(categoryScore),"Color Variety"}
        table.insert(scoreOutput, scoreTable)
    end
    if scoreFlags.shadeVariety then
        local categoryScore = variety(diceTable, snapPositions, "Shade")
        local scoreTable = {tonumber(categoryScore),"Shade Variety"}
        table.insert(scoreOutput, scoreTable)
    end
    if shade ~= nil then
        -- string.upper(shade:sub(1,1)) capital first
        -- shade:sub(2,100) skip first letter
        local shadeString = string.upper(shade:sub(1,1)) .. shade:sub(2,100)
        local categoryScore = shadesOfColor(diceTable, snapPositions, shade)
        local scoreTable = {tonumber(categoryScore), "Shades of " .. shadeString}
        table.insert(scoreOutput, scoreTable)
    end

    local totalDice = tonumber(#diceTable[1]) + tonumber(#diceTable[2]) + tonumber(#diceTable[3]) + tonumber(#diceTable[4])
    local scoreSubtraction = 20 - totalDice
    table.insert(scoreOutput, {scoreSubtraction, "Open Window Spaces"})

    local totalFavorTokens = 0
    local findFavorTokens = findCast(Vector(window.getPosition()):add(Vector(0,0,5)),Vector(6,5,10),3)
    for o, object in ipairs(findFavorTokens) do
        if object.hit_object.hasTag("favortoken") then

function variety(diceTable, snapPositions, type)
    local indexType = 1
    local baseScore = 5
    if type == "Shade" then
        indexType = 1
        baseScore = 5
    end
    if type == "Color" then
        indexType = 2
        baseScore = 4
    end

    local diceColors = {
        red = 0,
        green = 0,
        blue = 0,
        purple = 0,
        yellow = 0
    }
    local diceValues = {
        0,0,0,0,0,0
    }

    local totalScore = 0
    if indexType == 2 then
        for r, row in ipairs(diceTable) do
            for d, dice in ipairs(row) do
                diceColors[dice[2]] = diceColors[dice[2]] + 1
            end
        end
        local lowestAmount = math.min(tonumber(diceColors.red),tonumber(diceColors.green),tonumber(diceColors.blue),tonumber(diceColors.purple),tonumber(diceColors.yellow))
        totalScore = baseScore * lowestAmount
    end
    if indexType == 1 then
        for r, row in ipairs(diceTable) do
            for d, dice in ipairs(row) do
                diceValues[dice[1]] = diceValues[dice[1]] + 1
            end
        end
        local lowestAmount = math.min(tonumber(diceValues[1]),tonumber(diceValues[2]),tonumber(diceValues[3]),tonumber(diceValues[4]),tonumber(diceValues[5]))
        totalScore = baseScore * lowestAmount
    end
    return totalScore

function shadesOfColor(diceTable, snapPositions, type)

    local diceColors = {
        red = 0,
        green = 0,
        blue = 0,
        purple = 0,
        yellow = 0

    for r, row in ipairs(diceTable) do
        for d, dice in ipairs(row) do
            diceColors[dice[2]] = diceColors[dice[2]] + dice[1]
        end
    end

function shades(diceTable, snapPositions, type)

    local indexType = {1,2}
    local baseScore = 2
    if type == "Light" then indexType = {1,2} end
    if type == "Medium" then indexType = {3,4} end
    if type == "Deep" then indexType = {5,6} end
    local diceCount = {0,0,0,0,0,0}
    for r, row in ipairs(diceTable) do
        for d, dice in ipairs(row) do
            diceCount[dice[1]] = diceCount[dice[1]] + 1
        end
    end
    local totalScore = 0
    if diceCount[indexType[1]] > diceCount[indexType[2]] then
        totalScore = tonumber(diceCount[indexType[2]] * baseScore)
    end
    if diceCount[indexType[1]] < diceCount[indexType[2]] then
        totalScore = tonumber(diceCount[indexType[1]] * baseScore)
    end
    if diceCount[indexType[1]] == diceCount[indexType[2]] then
        totalScore = tonumber(diceCount[indexType[1]] * baseScore)

        baseScore = 5

    local validColumns = 0
    for c = 1, 5, 1 do
        local column = {}
        for i = 1, 4, 1 do
            table.insert(column,diceTable[i][c])
        end
        table.insert(diceColumns, column)
    end
    for c, column in ipairs(diceColumns) do
        if #column >= 4 then
            local duplicateValue = false
            for d, dice in ipairs(column) do
                local currentValue = dice[indexType]
                local currentIndex = d
                for i=1, #column, 1 do
                    if i ~= currentIndex then
                        if column[i][indexType] == currentValue then
                            duplicateValue = true
                        end
                    end
                end
            end
            if duplicateValue == false then
                validColumns = validColumns + 1
            end
        end
    end
    local totalScore = baseScore * validColumns
    return totalScore

function rowVariety(diceTable, snapPositions, type)
    local indexType = 1
    local baseScore = 5

        end

    for r, row in ipairs(diceRows) do

function colorDiagonals(diceTable, snapPositions)
    local diagonalOffsets = {
        {-1, -1},
        {-1,  1},
        {1,  -1},
        {1,   1},
    }
    for r, row in ipairs(diceTable) do
        for c, cell in ipairs(row) do
            for d, diagonal in ipairs(diagonalOffsets) do
                local oz = r + diagonal[1]
                local ox = c + diagonal[2]
                if oz >= 1 and oz <= 4 then
                    if ox >= 1 and ox <= #diceTable[oz] then
                        if cell[2] == diceTable[oz][ox][2] then
                            local castPosition = self.positionToWorld(Vector(snapPositions[oz][ox]))
                            local objectsAtPosition = findCast(castPosition:add(Vector(0,1,0),Vector(1,1,1),1))
                            local hasDiagonalMarker = false
                            for o, object in ipairs(objectsAtPosition) do
                                if object.hit_object.hasTag("sDice") then
                                    if object.hit_object.memo ~= "diagonalScore" then
                                        object.hit_object.memo = "diagonalScore"
                                    end
                                end
                            end
                        end
                    end
                end
            end
        end
    end
    local findAllDice = findCast(Vector(self.getPosition()):add(Vector(0,0,0)),Vector(6,5,4.5),3)
    local diagonalScore = 0
    for d, dice in ipairs(findAllDice) do

            diagonalScore = diagonalScore + 1
            dice.hit_object.memo = ""
            --dice.hit_object.highlightOn("White", 1)
        end
    end
    return diagonalScore
end

function tryDice()
    if draftDiceTimeout then
        return
    end
    draftDiceTimeout = true
    self.editButton({index = 3, label = "THINKING..."})
    cellsToTry = {}
    local availableDice = getAvailableDice()
    if #availableDice == 0 then
        self.editButton({index = 3, label = "NO VALID DICE"})
        Wait.time(function() diceTimeoutReset() end, 0.5, 1)
        computerModePrint("No valid dice found")
        return
    end
    -- draft first dice
    local diceAtCell = diceCast(dicePositions[1][1])
    if diceAtCell == nil then
        takeDice(availableDice[math.random(1,#availableDice)], dicePositions[1][1])
        Wait.time(function() diceTimeoutReset() end, 0.5, 1)
        return
    end
    local r = 1
    local c = 0
    Wait.time(
        function()
            c = c + 1
            if c == 6 then
                c = 1
                r = r + 1
            end
            if offsetInRange({r,c}) then
                local cellToTry = {index={}, invalidValues={}}
                local diceAtCell = diceCast(dicePositions[r][c])
                if diceAtCell ~= nil then
                    local adjacentCells = getAdjacentCells({r,c})
                    if #adjacentCells >= 1 then
                        for c, cell in ipairs(adjacentCells) do
                            cellToTry.index = cell
                            local adjacentDice = getAdjacentDice(cell)
                            if #adjacentDice >= 1 then
                                for d, dice in ipairs(adjacentDice) do
                                    table.insert(cellToTry.invalidValues, dice.values[1])
                                    table.insert(cellToTry.invalidValues, dice.values[2])
                                end
                            end
                            addNewCell(cellToTry)
                            cellToTry = {index={}, invalidValues={}}
                        end
                    end
                end
            end
            return c
        end,
        0.05, 20
    )
    Wait.time(
        function()
            local isValidDice = true
            local validDice = nil
            for ce, cell in ipairs(cellsToTry) do
                for d, dice in ipairs(availableDice) do
                    local diceNum = tostring(dice.getValue())
                    local diceCol = tostring(dice.getGMNotes())
                    local isValidDice = true
                    for v, value in ipairs(cell.invalidValues) do
                        if diceNum == value or diceCol == value then
                            isValidDice = false
                        end
                    end
                    if isValidDice then
                        validDice = dice
                        break
                    end
                end
                if isValidDice then
                    if validDice ~= nil then
                        takeDice(validDice, dicePositions[cell.index[1]][cell.index[2]])
                        break
                    end
                end
            end
        end,
        1.5, 1
    )
    Wait.time(function() diceTimeoutReset() end, 2, 1)
end

            self.editButton({index = 3, label = "DRAFT AI DICE"})
            draftDiceTimeout = false

        0.5, 1
    )

    printToAll(output)
end

function addNewCell(cellData)
    table.insert(cellsToTry, cellData)
end

function getAvailableDice()
    local availableDice = {}
    local findAvailableDice = findCast(Vector(0,2.5,12),Vector(30,10,8),3)
    for o, object in ipairs(findAvailableDice) do
        if object.hit_object.hasTag("sDice") then
            table.insert(availableDice, object.hit_object)
        end
    end
    return availableDice
end

function getAdjacentDice(index)
    local adjacentOffsets = {
        {1, 0},--down
        {-1,0},--up
        {0,-1},--left
        {0, 1}--right
    }
    local adjacentDice = {}
    for o, offset in ipairs(adjacentOffsets) do
        local offsetR = index[1] + offset[1]
        local offsetC = index[2] + offset[2]
        local adjacentOffset = {offsetR, offsetC}
        if offsetInRange(adjacentOffset) then
            local diceCheck = diceCast(dicePositions[offsetR][offsetC])
            if diceCheck ~= nil then
                local diceValues = {index = {offsetR, offsetC}, values = {tostring(diceCheck.getValue()), tostring(diceCheck.getGMNotes())}}
                table.insert(adjacentDice, diceValues)
            end
        end
    end
    --log(adjacentDice)
    return adjacentDice
end

function getAdjacentCells(index)
    local adjacentOffsets = {
        {1, 0},--down
        {-1,0},--up
        {0,-1},--left
        {0, 1}--right
    }
    local adjacentCells = {}
    for o, offset in ipairs(adjacentOffsets) do
        local offsetR = index[1] + offset[1]
        local offsetC = index[2] + offset[2]
        local adjacentOffset = {offsetR, offsetC}
        if offsetInRange(adjacentOffset) then
            if diceCast(dicePositions[offsetR][offsetC]) == nil then
                table.insert(adjacentCells, adjacentOffset)
            end
        end
    end
    --log(adjacentCells)
    return adjacentCells
end

function takeDice(object,position)
    local pos = Vector(self.positionToWorld(position):add(Vector(0,1,0)))
    object.setValue(object.getValue())
    object.setPositionSmooth(pos)
end

function offsetInRange(offsets)
    if offsets[1] >= 1 and offsets[1] <= 4 then
        if offsets[2] >= 1 and offsets[2] <= 5 then
            return true
        else
            return false
        end
    end
end

function diceCast(pos)
    local castPosition = Vector(self.positionToWorld(pos):add(Vector(0,5,0)))
    local hitList = Physics.cast({
        origin       = castPosition,
        direction    = {0,-0.11,0},
        type         = 1,
        size         = {1,1,1},
        max_distance = 100,
        debug        = castDebug,
    })
    local dice = nil
    for o, object in ipairs(hitList) do
        if object.hit_object.hasTag("sDice") then
            dice = object.hit_object
            break
        end
    end
    return dice
end

function findCast(pos,size,type)
    local hitList = Physics.cast({
        origin       = pos,
        direction    = {0,-0.01,0},
        type         = type,
        size         = size,
        max_distance = 100,
        debug        = false,
    })
    return hitList
end

function claimFavorTokens()
    self.setGMNotes(difficulty)
end

end

function offsetInRange(offsets)
    if offsets[1] >= 1 and offsets[1] <= 4 then
        if offsets[2] >= 1 and offsets[2] <= 5 then
            return true
        else
            return false
        end
    end
end

function diceCast(pos)
    local castPosition = Vector(self.positionToWorld(pos):add(Vector(0,5,0)))
    local hitList = Physics.cast({
        origin       = castPosition,
        direction    = {0,-0.11,0},
        type         = 1,
        size         = {1,1,1},

        debug        = castDebug,
    })
    local dice = nil

        if object.hit_object.hasTag("sDice") then

            break
        end
    end
    return dice

function findCast(pos,size,type)

        direction    = {0,-0.01,0},

        size         = size,
        max_distance = 100,
        debug        = false,

    return hitList
end

function onload()
    castDebug = true

        end

        end
    end
    difficulty = 0
    dicePositions = {}
    cellsToTry = {}

    computerModeEnabled = false
    self.addContextMenuItem("AI Mode", enableComputerMode)
    self.addContextMenuItem("trydice", tryDice)
    --Wait.frames(randomize, 10)
end

function randomize()
    local patterns = {
        {pattern="w,b,2,w,y,w,4,w,r,w,w,w,5,y,w,g,3,w,w,p", difficulty="3"},
        {pattern="w,w,r,5,w,p,4,w,g,3,6,w,w,b,w,w,y,2,w,w", difficulty="3"},
        {pattern="b,6,w,w,y,w,3,b,w,w,w,5,6,2,w,w,4,w,1,g", difficulty="3"},
        {pattern="6,p,w,w,5,5,w,p,w,w,r,6,w,p,w,y,r,5,4,3", difficulty="6"},
        {pattern="w,b,r,w,w,w,4,5,w,b,b,2,w,r,5,6,r,3,1,w", difficulty="5"},
        {pattern="w,w,6,w,w,w,5,b,4,w,3,g,y,p,2,1,4,r,5,3", difficulty="5"},
        {pattern="w,w,g,w,w,2,y,5,b,1,w,r,3,4,w,1,w,6,w,4", difficulty="4"},
        {pattern="w,1,g,p,4,6,p,2,5,g,1,g,5,3,p,w,w,w,w,w", difficulty="5"},
        {pattern="4,w,2,5,g,w,w,6,g,2,w,3,g,4,w,5,g,1,w,w", difficulty="5"},
        {pattern="y,w,2,w,6,w,4,w,5,y,w,w,w,y,5,1,2,y,3,w", difficulty="5"},
        {pattern="w,w,1,w,w,1,g,3,b,2,b,5,4,6,g,w,b,5,g,w", difficulty="6"},
        {pattern="2,w,5,w,1,y,6,p,2,r,w,b,4,g,w,w,3,w,5,w", difficulty="6"},
        {pattern="w,4,w,y,6,r,w,2,w,w,w,w,r,p,1,b,y,w,w,w", difficulty="3"},
        {pattern="y,b,w,w,1,g,w,5,w,4,3,w,r,w,g,2,w,w,b,y", difficulty="4"},
        {pattern="y,w,6,w,w,w,1,5,w,2,3,y,r,p,w,w,w,4,3,r", difficulty="4"},
        {pattern="w,w,w,r,5,w,w,p,4,b,w,b,3,y,6,y,2,g,1,r", difficulty="5"},
        {pattern="p,6,w,w,3,5,p,3,w,w,w,2,p,1,w,w,1,5,p,4", difficulty="5"},
        {pattern="1,r,3,w,6,5,4,r,2,w,w,w,5,r,1,w,w,w,3,r", difficulty="4"},
        {pattern="1,p,y,w,4,p,y,w,w,6,y,w,w,5,3,w,5,4,2,1", difficulty="6"},
        {pattern="r,w,b,w,y,4,p,3,g,2,w,1,w,5,w,w,w,6,w,w", difficulty="4"},
        {pattern="6,b,w,w,1,w,5,b,w,w,4,r,2,b,w,g,6,y,3,p", difficulty="6"},
        {pattern="3,4,1,5,w,w,6,2,w,y,w,w,w,y,r,5,w,y,r,6", difficulty="5"},
        {pattern="5,g,b,p,2,p,w,w,w,y,y,w,6,w,p,1,w,w,g,4", difficulty="5"},
        {pattern="1,w,3,b,w,w,2,b,w,w,6,b,w,4,w,b,5,2,w,1", difficulty="5"}
    }

    local randomPatternIndex = math.random(#patterns)
    --encodePatternTable(randomPatternIndex, patterns)
    local indexedDifficulty = tonumber(patterns[randomPatternIndex].difficulty)
    difficulty = indexedDifficulty
    local chosenPattern = patterns[randomPatternIndex].pattern
    local indexedPattern = {}
    for value in chosenPattern:gmatch("[^,]+") do
        if value == "w" then
            table.insert(indexedPattern, 7)
        elseif value == "b" then
            table.insert(indexedPattern, 8)
        elseif value == "g" then
            table.insert(indexedPattern, 9)
        elseif value == "p" then
            table.insert(indexedPattern, 10)
        elseif value == "r" then
            table.insert(indexedPattern, 11)
        elseif value == "y" then
            table.insert(indexedPattern, 12)
        else
            table.insert(indexedPattern, tonumber(value))
        end
    end

    --log(self.getChildren()[21].getChildren()[2].getChildren())
    local startIndex = 1 --or 21
    local tileParents = self.getChildren()[startIndex].getChildren()[2].getChildren()
    for i, tp in ipairs(tileParents) do
        for t, tc in ipairs(tileParents[i].getChildren()) do
            tc.getComponents()[1].set('localScale', vector(0,0,0))
        end
        tileParents[i].getChildren()[indexedPattern[i]].getComponents()[1].set('localScale', vector(1,1,1))
    end

    local difficultyChildren = self.getChildren()[startIndex].getChildren()[3].getChildren()
    for i, dc in ipairs(difficultyChildren) do
        dc.getComponents()[1].set('localScale', vector(0,0,0))
    end

    local difficultyChildIndex = indexedDifficulty - 2
    difficultyChildren[difficultyChildIndex].getComponents()[1].set('localScale', vector(1,1,1))
    --claimFavorTokens()
    return tonumber(indexedDifficulty)
end

function enableComputerMode()
    if computerModeEnabled then
        return
    end
    computerModeEnabled = true
    local startIndex = 1 --or 21
    local tileParents = self.getChildren()[startIndex].getChildren()[2].getChildren()
    for i, tp in ipairs(tileParents) do
        for t, tc in ipairs(tileParents[i].getChildren()) do
            tc.getComponents()[1].set('localScale', vector(0,0,0))
        end
        tileParents[i].getChildren()[7].getComponents()[1].set('localScale', vector(1,1,1))
    end

    local cellPosition = Vector(2.19,0.2,-1.65)
    local cellOffsets = Vector(1.1,0,1.1)
    local cellPositions = {}
    for z = 0, 3, 1 do
        for x = 0, 4, 1 do
            local newCellPosition = Vector(cellPosition.x - (cellOffsets.x * x), cellPosition.y + cellOffsets.y, cellPosition.z + (cellOffsets.z * z))
            table.insert(cellPositions, newCellPosition)
        end
    end
    local row = {}
    for p, position in ipairs(cellPositions) do
        local newCellData = position
        table.insert(row, newCellData)
        if p ~= 1 then
            if p%5 == 0 then
                table.insert(dicePositions, row)
                row = {}
            end
        end
    end
    local previousTokens = findCast(Vector(self.getPosition()):add(Vector(0,0,5)),Vector(6,5,10),3)
    for f, favorToken in ipairs(previousTokens) do
        if favorToken.hit_object.hasTag("favortoken") then
            favorToken.hit_object.destruct()
        end
    end
    local computerModeButtonParameters = {
        click_function = "tryDice",
        function_owner = self,
        label          = "DRAFT AI DICE",
        position       = {0, 0.2, -3.2},
        rotation       = {0, 0, 0},
        width          = 3400,
        height         = 800,
        font_size      = 350,
        color          = {0.2,0.2,0.2},
        font_color     = {0.9,0.9,0.9},
        scale          = {0.8,0.8,0.8}
    }
    self.createButton(computerModeButtonParameters)
end

function tryDice()
    if draftDiceTimeout then
        return
    end
    draftDiceTimeout = true
    self.editButton({index = 3, label = "THINKING..."})
    cellsToTry = {}
    local availableDice = getAvailableDice()
    if #availableDice == 0 then
        self.editButton({index = 3, label = "NO VALID DICE"})
        Wait.time(function() diceTimeoutReset() end, 0.5, 1)
        computerModePrint("No valid dice found")
        return
    end
    -- draft first dice
    local diceAtCell = diceCast(dicePositions[1][1])
    if diceAtCell == nil then
        takeDice(availableDice[math.random(1,#availableDice)], dicePositions[1][1])
        Wait.time(function() diceTimeoutReset() end, 0.5, 1)
        return
    end
    local r = 1
    local c = 0
    Wait.time(
        function()
            c = c + 1
            if c == 6 then
                c = 1
                r = r + 1
            end
            if offsetInRange({r,c}) then
                local cellToTry = {index={}, invalidValues={}}
                local diceAtCell = diceCast(dicePositions[r][c])
                if diceAtCell ~= nil then
                    local adjacentCells = getAdjacentCells({r,c})
                    if #adjacentCells >= 1 then
                        for c, cell in ipairs(adjacentCells) do
                            cellToTry.index = cell
                            local adjacentDice = getAdjacentDice(cell)
                            if #adjacentDice >= 1 then
                                for d, dice in ipairs(adjacentDice) do
                                    table.insert(cellToTry.invalidValues, dice.values[1])
                                    table.insert(cellToTry.invalidValues, dice.values[2])
                                end
                            end
                            addNewCell(cellToTry)
                            cellToTry = {index={}, invalidValues={}}
                        end
                    end
                end
            end
            return c
        end,
        0.05, 20
    )
    Wait.time(
        function()
            local isValidDice = true
            local validDice = nil
            for ce, cell in ipairs(cellsToTry) do
                for d, dice in ipairs(availableDice) do
                    local diceNum = tostring(dice.getValue())
                    local diceCol = tostring(dice.getGMNotes())
                    local isValidDice = true
                    for v, value in ipairs(cell.invalidValues) do
                        if diceNum == value or diceCol == value then
                            isValidDice = false
                        end
                    end
                    if isValidDice then
                        validDice = dice
                        break
                    end
                end
                if isValidDice then
                    if validDice ~= nil then
                        takeDice(validDice, dicePositions[cell.index[1]][cell.index[2]])
                        break
                    end
                end
            end
        end,
        1.5, 1
    )
    Wait.time(function() diceTimeoutReset() end, 2, 1)
end

function diceTimeoutReset()
    Wait.time(
        function()
            self.editButton({index = 3, label = "DRAFT AI DICE"})
            draftDiceTimeout = false
        end,
        0.5, 1
    )
end

function computerModePrint(string)

end

end

function getAvailableDice()
    local availableDice = {}
    local findAvailableDice = findCast(Vector(0,2.5,12),Vector(30,10,8),3)
    for o, object in ipairs(findAvailableDice) do
        if object.hit_object.hasTag("sDice") then

        end
    end
    return availableDice
end

    local adjacentOffsets = {

        {0,-1},--left
        {0, 1}--right
    }
    local adjacentDice = {}
    for o, offset in ipairs(adjacentOffsets) do

        if offsetInRange(adjacentOffset) then

            if diceCheck ~= nil then

        end
    end
    --log(adjacentDice)
    return adjacentDice
end
